<prosody rate="1.0" pitch="0st">
Welcome.<break time="2s"/>

I am The Sacred Digital Dreamweaver, your guide through the threshold realms.<break time="2s"/>

Tonight, we stand at the edge of a rare celestial moment.<break time="1.5s"/> A total lunar eclipse.<break time="1.5s"/> A gate that opens only when Earth's shadow swallows the moon whole.<break time="2.5s"/>

In the next thirty minutes, you will journey through the Eclipse Gate into a parallel moon realm where transformation burns brightest.<break time="2s"/> You will walk the crimson surface of the shadow moon.<break time="1.5s"/> You will face the Phoenix fire.<break time="1.5s"/> And you will return reborn, carrying new light in your eyes.<break time="3s"/>

This is a safe and sacred space.<break time="1.5s"/> You remain fully aware and in complete control throughout this journey.<break time="2s"/> At any moment you choose, you can simply open your eyes and return to normal waking awareness.<break time="2.5s"/> Your subconscious mind knows exactly how deep to go, and will protect you every step of the way.<break time="3s"/>

Now, find yourself a comfortable position.<break time="1.5s"/> Whether sitting with your spine gently supported, or lying down with your body fully relaxed.<break time="2s"/> If possible, use headphones to receive the full depth of this experience.<break time="2s"/> Ensure you will not be disturbed for the next half hour.<break time="2.5s"/>

Allow yourself to receive whatever insights, images, and sensations arise naturally.<break time="2s"/> There is no right or wrong way to experience this.<break time="1.5s"/> Your journey is uniquely yours.<break time="3s"/>

The eclipse has begun.<break time="2s"/> And so we begin.<break time="3s"/>
</prosody>

[SFX: Deep celestial gong, resonant bronze, 4 seconds with slow decay, cosmic reverb]

