<prosody rate="1.0" pitch="0st">
In a moment, I will count upward from one to five.<break time="2s"/> With each number, you will become more alert, more present, more awake, bringing back with you all the gifts, all the light, all the transformation you have claimed tonight.<break time="4s"/>

One.<break time="1.5s"/> Beginning to return now.<break time="2s"/> You feel sensation returning to your fingers and toes, a gentle tingling, a warmth.<break time="3s"/>

Two.<break time="1.5s"/> Deepening your breath, feeling your lungs expand and contract, oxygen flowing into your bloodstream, waking you gently from within.<break time="3s"/>

Three.<break time="1.5s"/> Awareness spreading through your entire body now, muscles gently reawakening, energy flowing, vitality returning.<break time="3s"/>

Four.<break time="1.5s"/> Almost fully present, you can feel the surface beneath you, the air on your skin, the sounds of the world around you becoming clearer.<break time="3s"/>

And five.<break time="2s"/> Eyes open, fully awake, fully here, feeling refreshed, renewed, and powerfully alive.<break time="4s"/>

Welcome back.<break time="3s"/>

Take a moment to stretch if you need to.<break time="2s"/> Roll your shoulders.<break time="1.5s"/> Wiggle your fingers and toes.<break time="2s"/> Come fully back into your physical body.<break time="3s"/>

And as you move through the hours, days, and weeks ahead, you now carry five sacred anchors to reconnect you to this transformation whenever you need them.<break time="4s"/>

<emphasis level="moderate">First</emphasis>, whenever you take three slow, deep breaths in succession, you will feel the warmth of the Phoenix fire rekindling in your chest, reminding you of your inner strength and your capacity to transform.<break time="4s"/>

<emphasis level="moderate">Second</emphasis>, whenever you notice the moon in the night sky, whether full or crescent or dark, you will remember the journey you took to the Red Moon, and you will feel a deep sense of connection to cycles of release and rebirth.<break time="4s"/>

<emphasis level="moderate">Third</emphasis>, whenever you place your hand over your heart and close your eyes for just a moment, you will feel the steady glow of your Inner Light, the truth of who you are beneath all masks and armor.<break time="4s"/>

<emphasis level="moderate">Fourth</emphasis>, whenever you see the color red, crimson, scarlet, you will recall the purging fire and know that what no longer serves you has been burned away, and you are free.<break time="4s"/>

And <emphasis level="moderate">fifth</emphasis>, whenever you feel the warmth of sunlight on your face, you will remember that you are reborn, radiant, and powerful beyond measure.<break time="4s"/>

These anchors are yours now.<break time="2s"/> They will serve you well.<break time="3s"/>

Thank you for walking this journey with me tonight.<break time="2s"/> Thank you for your courage, your openness, your willingness to step through the Eclipse Gate and claim your transformation.<break time="3.5s"/>

If this journey has served you, I invite you to share it, to like this pathworking, to subscribe for more sacred journeys, and to follow the links in the description to explore further realms of consciousness and transformation.<break time="4s"/>

Until we meet again, may you walk in light, may you burn with sacred fire, and may your eyes always glow with the power of who you truly are.<break time="4s"/>

Blessed be.<break time="3s"/>
</prosody>

